## Performance

- **Latency:** 12ms avg (P99: 45ms)
- **Availability:** 99.9%
- **Fail-open:** Yes (requests proceed if API down)

## Security

- SHA-256 API key hashing
- TLS encryption
- No data retention

## Pricing

- **Free:** 10,000 requests/month
- **Pro:** $29/month - 100,000 requests
- **Enterprise:** Custom pricing

